The paper deals with the problem of coordinating mobile robots on a graph, which is a common topic in multi-agent systems (MAS) and robotics. Therefore, cs.MA (Multiagent Systems) is the most likely category. The paper also involves algorithms and data structures, which are typical topics in Distributed Computing (cs.DC) and Data Structures and Algorithms (cs.DS). The problem of graph exploration and load balancing is related to Robotics (cs.RO), and the paper proposes algorithms for both synchronous and asynchronous systems, which is related to Systems and Control (cs.SY).
